data.description: Looking for a home to make your own? This is the one with 5 bedrooms and plenty of space to create your ideal space. The large fenced in backyard complete with a new shed and above ground pool is a great bonus in town. You are just minutes from shopping, the school, the zoo and more! The sewer line from the house was replaced just last year. This will be a great home for someone ready to put in a little work. It is being sold "as is".
